		<title>微軟與 OpenAI 協議 轉型營利公司估值上看 5,000 億美元</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/13/%e5%be%ae%e8%bb%9f%e8%88%87-openai-%e5%8d%94%e8%ad%b0-%e8%bd%89%e5%9e%8b%e7%87%9f%e5%88%a9%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e4%bc%b0%e5%80%bc%e4%b8%8a%e7%9c%8b-5000-%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83/</link>
		
